```c++
for(x=0,y=1;;x++){
    if(x%2==0) continue;
    y+=x;
    if(x==4) break;
}
```

```c++
for(x=1,y=2;x<4;x++){
    switch(x){
        case 1:
            y+=2;
        case 2:
            y+=x;
            break;
        default:
            y++;
    }
}
```
